> >>           high offset: 80 bytes
> >>           current:     280 bytes
> >>           lowest:      696 bytes
> >>           tracked:     696 bytes
> >>           untracked:   192 bytes
> >>           poisoned:    7220 bytes
> >>           low offset:  4 bytes
> >>         lkdtm: OK: the rest of the thread stack is properly erased
